    <item>
      <title>欧盟对苹果、谷歌、Meta 进行新数字法测试调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/apple-google-meta-probed-by-eu-in-test-of-new-digital-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着欧盟对苹果公司、Alphabet公司旗下谷歌和Meta Platforms公司是否遵守限制大型科技公司权力的严格新法律展开全面调查，它们面临着潜在巨额罚款的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/apple-google-meta-probed-by-eu-in-test-of-new-digital-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 10:06:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>天然气需求回升，中石油利润飙升创历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/petrochina-profits-surge-to-record-on-rebound-in-gas-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于天然气需求反弹帮助中国石油公司抵消了油价下跌的影响，该公司的年度利润升至历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/petrochina-profits-surge-to-record-on-rebound-in-gas-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 09:42:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于投资者权衡反对派的选举势头，塞内加尔债券下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/senegal-s-bonds-sink-as-investors-weigh-opposition-s-electoral-momentum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞内加尔的美元债券是周一新兴市场信贷中表现最差的债券之一，因为投资者在周日的选举后权衡反对派候选人赢得总统职位的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/senegal-s-bonds-sink-as-investors-weigh-opposition-s-electoral-momentum</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 09:32:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Northvolt 启动电池厂工作，为欧洲工业赢得胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/northvolt-starts-construction-of-5-billion-battery-plant-in-germany</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Northvolt AB 正在德国北部开始建设一座价值 50 亿欧元（合 54 亿美元）的电池厂，以供应电动汽车，这将结束新放宽的欧盟国家援助规则下激烈的游说努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/northvolt-starts-construction-of-5-billion-battery-plant-in-germany</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 09:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛经济学家表示，债券动荡终于减弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/turbulence-in-bonds-is-finally-abating-goldman-economists-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团表示，随着全球利率宽松周期的开始，固定收益市场的价格波动最终使隐含波动率达到 2008 年以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/turbulence-in-bonds-is-finally-abating-goldman-economists-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 09:19:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国最大矿业公司表示，在美国面临风险的情况下，该公司“将成为目标”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/major-chinese-miner-says-us-led-containment-is-risk-to-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国收购力度最大的金属集团之一、最大的上市矿业公司紫金矿业集团警告称，美国主导的解决北京对矿产控制问题的努力可能会减缓该公司的全球扩张，并警告称地缘政治紧张局势“正变得日益严峻”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/major-chinese-miner-says-us-led-containment-is-risk-to-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 06:52:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯袭击加剧全球紧张局势，油价连续三天下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-24/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-25</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯袭击事件后，地缘政治动荡不断升级，加上高盛集团对大宗商品前景看涨，石油期货价格上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-24/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-25</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 23:20:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
