      <title>由于交易员等待新的催化剂，股市回调：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-24/asian-shares-look-mixed-ahead-of-busy-data-week-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国股市在上周强劲反弹后预计低开，因为投资者在美国发布的关键数据之前评估了企业盈利前景，这些数据可能为美联储的政策路径提供进一步的线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-24/asian-shares-look-mixed-ahead-of-busy-data-week-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 22:41:33 GMT</pubDate>
